  <a class="dash-card warn dashboard-card-link" href="#vendorRequests" data-panel="vendorRequests"><%-alertDot(S.pendingVendorRequests)%><b>수정요청 대기</b><strong class="<%=level(S.pendingVendorRequests)%>"><%=num(S.pendingVendorRequests)%></strong></a>
  <a class="dash-card warn dashboard-card-link" href="#adCenter" data-panel="adCenter"><%-alertDot((S.pendingAdRequests||0)+(S.pendingBannerRequests||0))%><b>광고/배너 신청</b><strong class="<%=level((S.pendingAdRequests||0)+(S.pendingBannerRequests||0))%>"><%=num((S.pendingAdRequests||0)+(S.pendingBannerRequests||0))%></strong></a>
  <a class="dash-card alert dashboard-card-link" href="#adCenter" data-panel="adCenter"><%-alertDot(S.waitingPayments)%><b>입금확인 대기</b><strong class="<%=level(S.waitingPayments)%>"><%=num(S.waitingPayments)%></strong></a>
</div>
<div class="dash-grid">
