ve-btn">입금확인</button></form><%}else{%><span class="pending">입금대기</span><%}%><form method="post" action="/admin/ad-requests/<%=x.id%>/reject" class="report-done-form" style="margin-top:8px"><input name="admin_memo" placeholder="반려 사유"><button class="reject-btn">반려</button></form><form method="post" action="/admin/ad-requests/<%=x.id%>/cancel" class="report-done-form" style="margin-top:8px"><input name="admin_memo" placeholder="취소 메모"><button class="cancel-edit">취소</button></form><%}else{%>처리완료<%}%></td></tr><%})%></table></section><section id="revenue" class="panel admin-panel">
